entries.name: APPEND
entries.summary: If file doesn't exist, create one; if it does, append new contents to the end. File is in WRITE mode.

entries.name: CREATE
entries.summary: If file doesn't exist, create one; if it does, truncate the contents. File is in WRITE mode.

entries.name: OPEN
entries.summary: Open an existing file. If it doesn't exist, throw IOException. File is in READ mode.

name: FileMode
summary: The mode to open a stream from a file.
